    <h1>About Everlane Realty</h1>
    <p class="lede lede--wide">Everlane Realty is an independent, broker-owned real estate brokerage in downtown St. Petersburg &mdash; one licensed broker, working the market he lives in, backed by a knowledge base the brokerage keeps current so the advice you get is researched, not guessed.</p>
